name: "I've Got Your Back"
description: Okay, this is my very first piece on Hic Et Nunc, and it has a bit of a story. A few weeks ago, I gifted an OpenSea mint of this piece to a person who fooled me into thinking they were my friend. They blocked me, and I had no way of getting it back. As such, I think it's only fair to mint it again, and know that it will go to a much better owner. Thank you all for reading this!  The full story: https://twitter.com/cryptopom1/status/1373957701416448000
